procedure cpro001
* CLASIFICA ARCHIVO SPMATRI POR TITULO Y  MATRICULA
* SELECCIONANDO HABILITADOS > 2015
set exclusive on
use spmasor
set date to dmy
set century on
zap
*USE spmatri
use spmatri
set delete on
set talk off
sort to spmasor on titulo, numero for habili > 2020 and catego='A ' and vtohab>{28/06/2021} and condic<'2'
 